title: Dash Go Rapid Egg Cooker
description: The Dash Rapid Egg Cooker allows you to cook eggs in less time than it takes to boil water on a stove! Boiling tray holds up to 6 eggs, and separate non-stick poaching tray can poach up to 2 eggs. You can also make individual omelets or scrambled eggs! Features an On/Off button, BPA-free plastic egg holders for hard boiled eggs, poaching tray, measuring cup, and clear lid. Don’t be stuck waiting for water to boil; make the Dash Rapid Egg Cooker a staple of your kitchen!
